{"word":"H3915 - לַיִל - layil - lah'-yil - Night - இரவு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>לַיִל"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>layil"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>lah'-yil"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Night / இரவு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"இரவ, இராக்காலம், இராத்திரி, ஜாமம், இருட்டு, இருள் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"night (used of gloom, protective shadow) (figurative)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From the same as <a href=\"#/H3883 - לוּל - lûwl - lool/3883\">H3883</a>; properly a <i>twist</i> (away of the light), that is, <i>night</i>; figuratively <i>adversity: - </i>([mid-]) night (season)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3912 - לְטוּשִׁם - Lᵉṭûwshim - let-oo-sheem'/3912\">H3912</a>, <a href=\"#/H3913 - לָטַשׁ - lâṭash - law-tash'/3913\">H3913</a>, <a href=\"#/H3915 - לַיִל - layil - lah'-yil/3915\">H3915</a>, <a href=\"#/H3917 - לִילִית - lîylîyth - lee-leeth'/3917\">H3917</a>"}]}